# IssueFlow project context

## Stack
- Java 21, Spring Boot 3.4.2, Spring Data JPA (Hibernate 6), Spring Security, Spring Validation.
- PostgreSQL 16 via Docker Compose (`compose.yml`).
- Build: Maven via `./mvnw`. Tests: JUnit 5 + AssertJ + Mockito + Spring Boot Test slices.
- Lombok for boilerplate (constructors, getters, builders).

## Package layout (`com.att.tdp.issueflow`)
```
common/
  entity/BaseEntity.java                  # id, createdAt, updatedAt
  exception/                              # NotFoundException, ConflictException, ValidationException, ...
  web/GlobalExceptionHandler.java
  web/ApiError.java                       # error envelope DTO
  web/ErrorCode.java                      # stable UPPER_SNAKE_CASE codes
  enums/                                  # Role, TicketStatus, Priority, TicketType, AuditAction, Actor
config/
  SecurityConfig.java
  JpaConfig.java                          # @EnableJpaAuditing, @EnableTransactionManagement
  AsyncConfig.java                        # @EnableScheduling
  OpenApiConfig.java                      # optional (springdoc)
security/
  jwt/JwtService.java
  jwt/JwtAuthenticationFilter.java
  jwt/TokenDenyListService.java           # in-memory, behind interface
  CurrentUserService.java
user/
  User.java, UserRepository.java, UserService.java, UserController.java, dto/...
auth/
  AuthController.java, dto/LoginRequest.java, dto/LoginResponse.java
project/
  Project.java, ProjectRepository.java, ProjectService.java, ProjectController.java, dto/...
ticket/
  Ticket.java, TicketRepository.java, TicketService.java, TicketController.java, dto/...
comment/
  Comment.java, CommentRepository.java, CommentService.java, CommentController.java, dto/...
audit/
  AuditLog.java, AuditLogRepository.java, AuditLogService.java, AuditLogController.java, dto/...
dependency/
  TicketDependency.java, TicketDependencyRepository.java, TicketDependencyService.java, TicketDependencyController.java
attachment/
  Attachment.java, AttachmentRepository.java, AttachmentService.java, AttachmentController.java
mention/
  Mention.java, MentionRepository.java, MentionService.java, MentionController.java
csv/
  TicketCsvController.java, TicketCsvService.java
schedule/
  EscalationJob.java
IssueFlowApplication.java
```

## Module template
Every feature package exposes: `<Entity>.java`, `<Entity>Repository.java`, `<Feature>Service.java`, `<Feature>Controller.java`, a `dto/` subpackage, and colocated `*Test.java` files under `src/test/java/...`.

## Spec contract
The single source of truth for endpoints is `README.md`. Mirror its paths and payload shapes exactly, even if they look non-RESTy (e.g. `POST /users/update/:userId`).
